In any of the following situations, Agora recommends that your server regenerate the Token and then call this method to pass in the new Token:


When receiving the  callback indicating that the Token is about to expire;

When receiving the  callback indicating that the Token has expired;

When receiving the  callback reporting ConnectionChangedTokenExpired (9);

In any of the following cases, Agora recommends that your server regenerate a token and then call this method to pass in the new token:


When receiving the  callback indicating the token is about to expire;

When receiving the  callback indicating the token has expired;

When receiving the  callback with ConnectionChangedTokenExpired(9);

In any of the following situations, Agora recommends that you regenerate a token on your server and call this method to pass in the new token:


When you receive the  callback indicating the token is about to expire;

When you receive the  callback indicating the token has expired;

When you receive the  callback reporting connectionChangedTokenExpired (9);

